    "causal_summary": "Codex (OpenAI's coding agent) misinterprets agent routing metadata in `/create` command `.md` and `.yaml` files as dispatch instructions, causing unintended agent invocations. This spec applied the same three-pronged compatibility strategy from spec 010 (spec_kit commands) to all 20 create command files, and additionally cleaned up stale emoji optionality language aligned with spec 011.",
